{"tid":157594,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"概率問題","createTime":"2017-03-15T15:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T07:30:42.000Z","uid":8540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b66eb1c40a18ad8c5ae2300f80ebc2694a2505","tid":157594,"uid":8540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"According to the past records about the customers in City P, 54% of them went to Shop X and 43% of them went to Shop Z. In addition, 20% of them went to both Shop X and Shop Y while 88% of them went to Shop X or Shop Y. A group of new customers has just arrived at City P and one of them is randomly selected. Based on the given informational:<br />\n<br />\na) Find the probability that the customer will go to Shop Y.<br />\n<br />\nb) Knowing that the customer will not go to Shop X, find the probability that he will not go to Shop Y neither.<br />\n<br />\nc) Suppose that the probability that a customer will not go to Shop X given that he will go to Shop Z is 0.37 Find the probability that he will go to Shop X but not Shop Z.<br />\n<br />\n幫朋友問求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2943578e3d6aa8d99a36c7147c4ea223a82bc3","tid":157594,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc2ded5d636dc9317dbb05cee26d15da9e21a95e","tid":157594,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"(a)<br />\nP(X or Y) = P(X) + P(Y) - P(XY)<br />\nP(Y) = 0.88-0.54+0.2 = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(b)<br />\nP(Yc | Xc) = P(Yc,Xc)/P(Xc) = (1-0.54)^2/(1-0.54) = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(c)<br />\n<br />\nP(X,Zc) = (1-0.37)*0.43 = 0.2709<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbeaf0cdc1103d02179b9bda2fe740e9fe59c7b","tid":157594,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"Too long can't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c340b80a68838a48b185cd0e9ba34be302d42a1d","tid":157594,"uid":63563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(a)<br />\nP(X or Y) = P(X) + P(Y) - P(XY)<br />\nP(Y) = 0.88-0.54+0.2 = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(b)<br />\nP(Yc | Xc) = P(Yc,Xc)/P(Xc) = (1-0.54)^2/(1-0.54) = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(c)<br />\n<br />\nP(X,Zc) = (1-0.37)*0.43 = 0.2709<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nb果度 P(yc,xc) = 1-P(y or x)<br />\n答案係(1-0.88)/(1-0.54) <br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"15d8355fd0234e650844eaa92758426c81733877","tid":157594,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>(a)<br />\nP(X or Y) = P(X) + P(Y) - P(XY)<br />\nP(Y) = 0.88-0.54+0.2 = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(b)<br />\nP(Yc | Xc) = P(Yc,Xc)/P(Xc) = (1-0.54)^2/(1-0.54) = 0.54<br />\n<br />\n(c)<br />\n<br />\nP(X,Zc) = (1-0.37)*0.43 = 0.2709<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nb果度 P(yc,xc) = 1-P(y or x)<br />\n答案係(1-0.88)/(1-0.54) <br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\nP(xc,yc) = 1 - P(y or x) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49a157134ce3913a5501d837c93485bd476fa53","tid":157594,"uid":63563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>(a)<br />\nP(X or Y) = P(X) 